unified code for units of measure.data-term: unified code for units of measure

examples.en: The Earth makes a yearly revolution around the Sun.
He gave yearly great sums in charity.
The city is celebrated for its yearly horse show.
Trade agreements are to be accounted for yearly.
She renews her lease on a yearly basis.
Salary levels are reviewed on a yearly basis.
She settled a small yearly sum on each of her children.
She went to the hospital for her yearly mammogram.
The company had yearly sales figures of half a million units.
The country is systematizing yearly exams for high-school students.
